Attribute.value: These characteristics confirm that these documents are likely being crafted using an automated builder. In more recent campaigns, the Microsoft Excel spreadsheets were crafted to make static analysis with tools like XLMDeobfuscator less effective.

Attribute.comment: example of the syntax used to execute the payload using rundll32.exe

Attribute.value:
The body of the HTTP POST request contains information about the victim system. The data sent to the C2 includes:

    %APPDATA% configuration.
    The hostname of the system.
    The username of the victim.
    The Workstation configuration of the system.
